This repository contains an evaluation pipeline, Dify template, prompts,
analysis files, and r1-r4 run artifacts for the RAG Eval JA Repro
reproducibility dataset:

  SakataConsul/rag-eval-ja-repro
  https://huggingface.co/datasets/SakataConsul/rag-eval-ja-repro

RAG Eval JA Repro is derived from:

  allganize/RAG-Evaluation-Dataset-JA
  https://huggingface.co/datasets/allganize/RAG-Evaluation-Dataset-JA

